## ததஅக

[ appuṟam ]  
  
s. விஉரி. (அ. dem.) that side  
further  
moreover  
henceforth  
yonder  
beyond  
அப்பாலே  
appram அப்பறம்  
1. that side; farther  
2. moreover; then  
afterwards; later  
3. [on the far side of  
beyond (post. + dat.)]  
4. after (post. + past pt.)  
[ appuṟm ]  
s. [used adverbially.]  
fur ther  
on that side  
furthermore  
afterward  
after that. பார். புறம். அப்புறத்துக்கப்புறம். let the future take care of itself